# init(empty:)

**Initializer**

Creates an empty sequence of strings or integers.

## Declaration

```swift
convenience init(empty type: MLFeatureType)
```

## Parameters

- **type**: An [doc://com.apple.coreml/documentation/CoreML/MLFeatureType] instance that determines the sequenceâ€™s element type, which must be either [doc://com.apple.coreml/documentation/CoreML/MLFeatureType/string] or [doc://com.apple.coreml/documentation/CoreML/MLFeatureType/int64].

## Creating a sequence

- **init(strings:)**: Creates a sequence of strings from a string array.
- **init(int64s:)**: Creates a sequence of integers from an array of numbers.
